<HEAD>Bodies of Couple, Two Children Found, Murder-Suicide Suspected</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: CORRECTS in summary line that bodies of two children, sted
four were found; SUBS 2nd graf to CORRECT that relative sted
neighbor spotted the bodies; SUBS grafs 4, `Lt. David ...,' and 7,
