``Not to my knowledge.''
   Glenn, who failed in a bid for the Democratic presidential
nomination in 1984, has not discouraged speculation about the No. 2
spot on the ticket.
   Dukakis has refused to be talk about who he might choose as his
running mate if nominated for president.
