   _East: Atlanta 61 fair; Boston 55 drizzle; Buffalo 53 cloudy;
Charleston, S.C. 62 showers; Cincinnati 53 fair; Cleveland 52
cloudy; Detroit 48 fair; Miami 69 fair; New York 55 foggy;
Philadelphia 57 cloudy; Pittsburgh 52 cloudy; Portland, Maine 45
drizzle; Washington 58 foggy.
