fair; Los Angeles 62 fair; Phoenix 81 fair; Salt Lake City 48 fair;
San Diego 65 fair; San Francisco 61 fair; Seattle 62 cloudy.
   _Canada: Montreal 55 showers; Toronto 48 partly cloudy.
