New York firm Wells, Rich, Green that showed people with multiple
sclerosis doing such activities as scuba diving and sky diving, she
changed her mind.
   Miss Rhue will appear in an ad sitting in a wheelchair. The
headline says ``Even With MS, Madlyn Rhue Is On a Roll.'' The print
ad campaign premieres this month.
   ``It says to the world, OK, I'm in a wheelchair,'' Miss Rhue
said, ``but look at what I can do.''
