<HEAD>Marines Conducting Field Exercise in Honduras</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A battalion of about 1,000 Marines will
conduct a training exercise in Honduras for the next two weeks, the
Pentagon said Wednesday.
   The Marine Air Contingency Battalion, dispatched from Camp
